🖥️ Fátima Click

Fátima Click is a website designed to provide information about Catholic events, including Mass schedules, prayers, and religious gatherings. The goal is to make it easier for the faithful to find relevant information and stay connected with their faith.

✨ Features

📅 Mass Schedules: Find Mass times for different churches.

🙏 Prayers: Access a collection of traditional Catholic prayers.

📢 Events: Stay updated on Catholic events and prayer gatherings.

🎨 User-Friendly Design: Simple and responsive layout using HTML, CSS, and Bootstrap.

🛠️ Technologies Used

HTML & CSS for structuring and styling the website.

Bootstrap for a responsive and modern design.

JavaScript for interactive elements.

🚀 How to Use

Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/joaolucaspfer/fatima-click.git

Open the index.html file in your browser to explore the site.

📫 Contact

For suggestions or collaboration, feel free to reach out!
